title: CSE: 2015-1009 - New Listing - Peak Positioning Technologies Inc. (PKK)
text:
October 21, 2015 14:13 ET CSE: 2015-1009 - New Listing - Peak Positioning Technologies Inc. (PKK) 
TORONTO, ONTARIO--(Marketwired - Oct. 21, 2015) - 
The common shares of Peak Positioning Technologies Inc. have been approved for listing on the CSE. 
Listing and disclosure documents will be available at thecse.com Trading Date: October 23, 2015 Symbol: PKK ISIN: CA 70469M 10 8 6 Boardlot: TBD 
Peak Positioning Technologies Inc. previously traded on the TSX Venture Exchange. Contact Information
